headline: Protocol Deterioration
content: Power levels for the Focus of Water appear stable. Initiating primal matrix. Commencing Hydris Protocols in 5… 4… 3… 2…. 1. Infusion process initiated. Cellular transformation in process. Subject’s vitals are normal… wait, we are seeing a psychological fluctuation. Attempting to normalize. Normalization failed. Oh, no. Primal matrix deteriorating. System overload imminent! Subject is… by the gods of Orias… run!
